Attention Members of UC Berkeley Memes for Edgy Teens:

It is with a heavy heart that we, the UC Berkeley Memes for Edgy Teens Administrative and Moderating team, announce the end of our sixty-seven year sponsorship with Sizzler™ (Now you're talking). It was not an easy decision and we hope that Sizzler™ (Now you're talking) gets their shit together and stops being a fucking dickwad. We appreciate all that Sizzler™ (Now you're talking) has done for UC Berkeley Memes for Edgy Teens during these amazing a 38 years and we hope to one day reunite. Until that time comes we will still be talking. 

In other news: we are now officially sponsored by Boot Barn, FOX, Circuit City, Netscape, and Shasta.

Your Truly,
Mike Honcho and the rest of the UC Berkeley Memes for Edgy Teens Team.
